{"tid":683794,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電視成日自動熄機","createTime":"2018-05-30T03:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T06:12:30.000Z","uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"121d39f09d524bbe9dbe17948ab54ee25ab84639","tid":683794,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T03:52:36.000Z","msg":"利申返先 唔係靈異野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n情況大概維持左接近一年<br />\n<br />\n個電視係最初代個隻LCD(我諗有十年以上)<br />\n<br />\n每逢去到放工時間打後就開始自動熄(日頭情況好好多，基本上成朝得一兩次)<br />\n<br />\n試過一開返又即刻熄<br />\n<br />\n亦都肯定唔關時間制事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以個人推測原因如下:<br />\n<br />\n1.隔黎屋remote太強影響到我屋企<br />\n(但係呢一年先有呢個問題)<br />\n<br />\n2.電視有零件壞左<br />\n<br />\n3.屋企wifi signal干擾到電視(有冇可能？)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求解決辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd436fbe987c91d082d5fd464688c54550ebfec","tid":683794,"uid":43046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T03:57:18.000Z","msg":"唔睇電視"},{"pid":"5505d258168492942ea580c70bcaedbbd867c5d5","tid":683794,"uid":8717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"121d39f09d524bbe9dbe17948ab54ee25ab84639","tid":683794,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T03:52:36.000Z","msg":"利申返先 唔係靈異野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n情況大概維持左接近一年<br />\n<br />\n個電視係最初代個隻LCD(我諗有十年以上)<br />\n<br />\n每逢去到放工時間打後就開始自動熄(日頭情況好好多，基本上成朝得一兩次)<br />\n<br />\n試過一開返又即刻熄<br />\n<br />\n亦都肯定唔關時間制事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以個人推測原因如下:<br />\n<br />\n1.隔黎屋remote太強影響到我屋企<br />\n(但係呢一年先有呢個問題)<br />\n<br />\n2.電視有零件壞左<br />\n<br />\n3.屋企wifi signal干擾到電視(有冇可能？)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求解決辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T03:58:48.000Z","msg":